headline: Humana Board Declares Payment of Quarterly Dividend to Stockholders
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., February 19, 2026--Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend to stockholders of $0.885 per share payable on April 24, 2026 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on March 27, 2026.

headline: Humana Expands Florida Primary Care As Shares Trade Below Targets
summary: Humana’s CenterWell unit has agreed to acquire MaxHealth to expand its primary care reach in Florida. The deal adds MaxHealth clinics to CenterWell’s network, increasing access to value based care for patients in key Florida markets. The transaction highlights Humana’s (NYSE:HUM) continued focus on primary care delivery and Medicare focused services.
